message:
Hi friends! I am posting again about gospel housing so fellow women listen up! 

The lighthouse IS for sure staying around next year! Currently we have about 11 girls that have or are signing next year. We still would love 7 more girls to fill it! So if you are interested, please feel free to contact me or Emily Wydo about seeing the house or any questions you might have! 

Message me or text me at 763-234-5586
